how to convert a list to a tuple
Use the tuple() function
my_list = [1, 2, 2, 3, 4]
my_tuple = tuple(my_list)
if you turned 1,2,2,3,4 into a tuple it would turn into 1,2,2,3,4

how to convert a list to set
use the set() function
my_list = [1, 2, 2, 3, 4]
my_set = set(my_list)
if you turned 1,2,2,3,4 into a set it would also turn into 1,2,3,4

